[[File:Cacti.jpg|thumb|right|200px|Three giant cacti.]]
'''Giant cacti''' grew on the [[Desert/Legends|desert]] [[Moon/Legends|moon]] of [[Yavin 13/Legends|Yavin 13]] in extensive forests. The [[Plant/Legends|plants]] were capable of reaching heights of 16 [[Meter/Legends|meters]], and protected themselves with spikes. They gathered [[Water/Legends|water]] from occasional storms, storing the liquid in their spongy leaves and stems for slow use in times of drought. They also grew deep roots to extract liquid from the soil.<ref name="GG2">''[[Galaxy Guide 2: Yavin and Bespin]]''</ref>

The [[Slith]] often rested in the shade cast by the tall plants.<ref name="GG2" />

